{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8d0c928f10","title":"大同战役后即准备平汉战役","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3a2b2c10cf","index":0,"year":1946,"month":8,"day":6,"articleId":"8d0c928f10"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"577f9f5537","type":"paragraph","text":"大同战役后即准备平汉战役口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"8d0c928f10"},{"id":"17edf9f5e2","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年8月6日）录：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"8d0c928f10"},{"id":"719accd820","type":"paragraph","text":"你在布置大同战役后，望集中注意于准备平汉战役。凡列入平汉战役序列之军队，迅即补充人员武器，训练攻城技术，司令部则完成侦察事项，拟定作战计划，务于未前完成一切准备事项，一候大同得手立即开始平汉作战","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"8d0c928f10"},{"id":"0b2fbf4d3b","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"8d0c928f10"},{"id":"f6c20b171a","type":"paragraph","text":"未鱼[I]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给晋察要军区司令员兼政治委员衰荣臻的电报。[2]1946年7月31日，晋缓军区、晋察冀军区各1部发起大同战役。至8月4日，开灭外围国民党军2000余人。8月14日开始夺取城关及郊区据点。9月初肃清郊区各据点及北关、西关国民党守军。后由于国民党军第十二战区3万余人于9月13日政占集宁增极大同，香绥和晋察冀军区部队迷于16日撤除了对大同的包围。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"8d0c928f10"}],"page":{"id":"514a338af7","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"8d0c928f10","start":43,"end":43}}}},"__N_SSG":true}